Enum Webhook.EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Webhook.EventType>
      • com.paymill.models.Webhook.EventType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Webhook.EventType>
    Enclosing class:
    Webhook

    public static enum Webhook.EventType
extends Enum<Webhook.EventType>
    There are a number of events you can react to. Each webhook can be configured to catch any kind of event individually, so you can create different webhooks for different events. Each Webhook needs to be attached to at least one event.
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Vassil Nikolov
